@startuml sequence_notes_template
!theme plain
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center

title Sequence — Create Notes File from Template

actor "Job Seeker" as User
participant "templates/\nnotes-template.md" as Template
participant "content/notes/" as Notes

User -> Template : Copy notes-template.md
Template --> User : Returns template\nwith required sections

User -> Notes : Save as\n<company>-<role>.md

User -> Notes : Fill in Role Snapshot
User -> Notes : Fill in Baseline Bullets
User -> Notes : Fill in Additional Bullet Bank
User -> Notes : Fill in Tailoring Angles
User -> Notes : Fill in Keyword Bank

Notes --> User : Notes file complete\nand conforming to template

@enduml
